aijinglengyan/status/1388645793729368066?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"a0d77d4168e3ef21dc718ceb569a7480f99f47a7","tid":2515104,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:07:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9d12fc8386a1d714eb632b14a6068cb80bf6e27","tid":2515104,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:08:09.000Z","msg":"In an exclusive interview with India Today TV, Mukesh Aghi said, &ldquo;Our challenge is logistics. We were sourcing most of these from China. <span class=\"red\">China, for whatever reason, has stopped all cargo flights into India.</span> One of our first consignments that landed in India had to be routed from Shanghai to Tokyo and then from Tokyo to Delhi. We are moving most from Shanghai to Dubai, Shanghai to Bangkok which just adds to the timeline.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nWhen asked about the disruption that came after China has pledged to help India, Aghi said &ldquo;One is action the other is words. Action is you stop the flights which is not helping, words is you deliver on them else it does not help. That is the difference.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5967a5ee424dba9e8fb0975f13ad202553066a8b","tid":2515104,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"支國一向就最仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d483e14247072e842887018833de479eea3c5862","tid":2515104,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"Retweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8478fbcad420510c1643507e9a5c057e888b9c","tid":2515104,"uid":152516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5967a5ee424d